official_title: A bill to authorize the acquisition of certain lands for addition to Rocky Mountain National Park in the State of Colorado.

summary.text: (LATEST SUMMARY) Authorizes the acquisition of lands for addition to the Rocky Mountain National Park in the State of Colorado. Authorizes to be appropriated $2,423,740 for land acquisition and $318,000 for development.
